Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL hostapd: Bug Fixes for AFC Random Channel
 Change

Following Bug Fixes for AFC Random Channel Change

1. When EIRP is same, give higher priority to full bandwidth
   channel compared to punctured channel.
2. Select least punctured channels for random channel selection.
3. Avoid puncturing in non 11be mode.
4. Avoid dynamic puncturing when strict puncturing is enable.

Feature: AFC
